      <head>nāgavarma viracita<lb
      />vardhamāna purāṇaṁ</head>
      <pb n="3"/>
      <div n="1" type="āśvāsaṁ">
	<head>prathamāśvāsaṁ</head>
	<lg n="1" met="sragdhare">
	  <l><note>īga doretiruva ī hastapratiya ondaneya patra idē hasta pratige sēridu dallavendu hēḷabēkāgide. ēkendare idaralli uḷida patragaḷigiruvante patra saṅkhyeyilla. munde 2neya patradinda kramavāda patra saṅkhyeyide. saṅkhyeyillada modala patradalli mūru padyagaḷiddu munde baravaṇigeyilla. 2neya patradalliyū svalpajāga khāli iddu illi koṭṭiruva 2neya padyadinda kāvyabhāga doreyuttade. mūlapratiyalli padyasaṅkhye gaḷilladiruvudarinda 2neya padyakke modalina eṣṭu padyagaḷu luptavāgiveyo tiḷiyadu. modala patradalli doreyuva mūru padyagaḷalli modala eraḍu padyagaḷu kramavāgi nēmicandrana līlāvati kāvśada modala padyavū, aggaḷana candraprabha purāṇada modala padyavū āgive. mūraneya padya vardhamānana stutiyannoḷagoṇḍiddu īga doretiruva yāva campūkr̥tigaḷalliyū doreyadiruvudarinda (śrī en. ananta raṅgācāryara kannaḍa campūkāvyagaḷa padyagaḷa akārādyanukramaṇiyante) idu prakr̥ta kāvyakke sēridudendu bhāvisi adannu illi modala padyavannāgiṭṭukoḷḷalāgide.</note>śrīmadbhavyāḷi cakraprakara sukhakaraṁ sarvamithyāndhakāra</l>
	  <l>stōmapradhvaṁsi bōdhāmaḷakiraṇa gaṇōdbhāsi mōkṣābjinī su</l>
	  <l>prēmaṁ syādvāda pūrvācaḷa samuditanāścaryavr̥ttābhirāmaṁ</l>
	  <l>hēmāṅgaṁ vardhamānāhimakaranatinirdōṣamaṁ māḻke nammoḷ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="2" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>aphavighaṭana kāraṇama</l>
	  <l>mmaghaṭita padabandha bandhurāḷaṅkr̥tiyaṁ</l>
	  <l>laghavāge pogaḻe pēḻdaṁ</l>
	  <l>raghuvaṁśa mahāpurāṇamaṁ śrīvijayaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="4"/>
	<lg n="3" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>sarasaprasanna mādhu</l>
	  <l>ryarañjitaṁ dravyamanvitārthamidene vi</l>
	  <l>staradiṁ harivaṁśakathāṁ</l>
	  <l>taramaṁ sogayisidanesevinaṁ guṇavarmaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="4" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>gadyadoḷaṁ padyadoḷaṁ</l>
	  <l>cōdyamidene vatsarāja caritāgamamaṁ</l>
	  <l>vidyānidhi baredaṁ nira</l>
	  <l>vadyagu<app><lem>ṇaṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">ṇani</rdg></app> nāgavarmanupacitaśarmaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="5" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>dhareyoḷage negaḻe śāntī</l>
	  <l>śvara va<app><lem>ra</lem><rdg wit="#M">dhu</rdg></app> katheyaṁ prarāṇacūḍāmaṇiyaṁ</l>
	  <l>viracisida ponnamayyane</l>
	  <l>caritārthaṁ kr̥ti kavīndracūḍāratnaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="6" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>ādijinanāthacaritama</l>
	  <l>nādammaidaccarītiyoḷ pudivinamu</l>
	  <l>tpādisida pampanantudi</l>
	  <l>tōdita <app><lem>mr̥du</lem><rdg wit="#M">mr̥...</rdg></app>vacana guṇpanāvanumoḷanē</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="7" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>pariṇata saṁskr̥ta padapoṁ</l>
	  <l>dire saundaramappa tiruḷa kannaḍadoḷ vi</l>
	  <l>starisidanajitajinēśvara</l>
	  <l>caritamanujvaḷayaśaṁ ma<app><lem>hāka</lem><rdg wit="#M">hā...</rdg></app>viratnaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="8" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>mr̥dusandarbhamudāttaṁ</l>
	  <l>sadaḷaṅkr̥tiyene sulōcanācaritamaniṁ</l>
	  <l>podevire pēḻdaṁ kavitā</l>
	  <l>vidagdha matiyenipa nāgadēvakavīndraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="5"/>
	<lg n="9" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>savi ni<app><lem>le bhā</lem><rdg wit="#M">le...</rdg></app>vadoḷ rasamadaggalisittu samasta kānti sau</l>
	  <l>ṣṭhavadoḍanondi nindudu padaṁ mr̥durītiyoḷādemimpuve</l>
	  <l>ttamardudu dēse mārgadoḷoḍambaḍanāṁ<app><lem>tudu ka</lem><rdg wit="#M">tu..</rdg></app>bbamintuṭa</l>
	  <l>kkume sarasārtha sārthamene pēḻvudu pēḻade pēḻvenembanuṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="10" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>padamalargaḷandadiṁ baṁ</l>
	  <l>dhada bigipinoḷondi nile samujvaḷakānti</l>
	  <l>pradamā....r gati same</l>
	  <l>vudumōleya teṟadinoppe kavi satkr̥tiya<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app></l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="11" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l><app><lem>oseduṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">...ṁ</rdg></app> naḍedoḍamarkeyi</l>
	  <l>nesedire sakkadadamardure kāñcanadoḷ kī</l>
	  <l>lisida kisuga<app><lem>llavol</lem><rdg wit="#M">....lu</rdg></app> raṁ</l>
	  <l>jisuguṁ kr̥ti samupalabdhabandhacchāyaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="12" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>posatenisuva bage mātina</l>
	  <l>pasu.....................................padabandhaṁ raṁ</l>
	  <l>jisuva rasaṁ bageyiṁ<app><lem>daṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app></l>
	  <l>posa<app><lem>ya</lem><rdg wit="#M">yi</rdg></app>tiyaṁ meccadippanāvanumoḷanē</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="13" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>rasavanmr̥dūkti vipuḷā</l>
	  <l>rtha samarpaṇa<app><lem>vondavinda</lem><rdg wit="#M">vendivondi</rdg></app> nileyumada<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> ma</l>
	  <l>nnisugume jagatījanamaṁ</l>
	  <l>prasādaguṇamilla<app><lem>dā</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>da satiyuṁ kr̥tiyuṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="14" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>vācaspatiyenisida kavi</l>
	  <l>tācaturaṁ pēḻda kabbamaṁ durjana hr̥</l>
	  <l>dgō<app><lem>ca</lem><rdg wit="#M">pa</rdg></app>ramāgaduḷūka vi</l>
	  <l>ḷōcanagōcaravināṁśuvāgada teṟadiṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="6"/>
	<lg n="15" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>ti....ti durmukhaṁ marma</l>
	  <l>vr̥ścananantaraṅgadhr̥takōpaṁ nāḷivraṇa</l>
	  <l>dantire keḷardu kavibhr̥</l>
	  <l>vanagardagardu dōṣa tatparanakkuṁ (?)</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="16" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>snigdhāmayamr̥tamenipaṁ</l>
	  <l>dagdhavaca....dukāramāṟisuva naraṁ</l>
	  <l>mugdha jana parama vāgviṣa</l>
	  <l>tigdha tiraskāramaḻalisal neṟedapudē</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="17" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>ajñā na pogarteyiṁ śā</l>
	  <l>strajñanr̥pāḷi<app><lem>yu</lem><rdg wit="#M">sadu</rdg></app>padēśamembante karaṁ</l>
	  <l>prājñaṅge bagedu nōḍe ma</l>
	  <l>nō<app><lem>jña</lem><rdg wit="#M">jñaṁ</rdg></app>ge praṇayānurāgamaṁ puṭṭi suguṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="18" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>bhēṣajadantire sujanaṁ</l>
	  <l>dōṣamanapaharisi guṇamanadaṟoḷe tōrkuṁ</l>
	  <l>māṣamukhadante kelar</l>
	  <l>dōṣagrāhigaḷaḍurtu kasavane piḍivar</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="19" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>madhyastha vr̥ttiyiṁ si</l>
	  <l>ddhādhyēyarenippa<app><lem>ri</lem><rdg wit="#M">ti</rdg></app>rdu tirdugema samā</l>
	  <l>tkr̥dyadbuddhi gaḷati du</l>
	  <l>rbodhyara<app><lem>dē</lem><rdg wit="#M">nē</rdg></app>nendu tirduvar satkr̥tiyaṁ	</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="20" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>avyutpannar bahudō</l>
	  <l>ṣavyasanar mandavakra<app><lem>ri</lem><rdg wit="#M">di</rdg></app>re tatsabheyoḷ</l>
	  <l>kāvyajña dhiṣaṇaremage gu</l>
	  <l>ṇavyakteyanuṇṭumāḍuganukūlateyiṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="7"/>
	<lg n="21" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>kathe gaṇabhr̥tpraṇītamitihāsa samudbhavamānatēndranī</l>
	  <l>kr̥tigadhināyakaṁ negaḻda vīrajinaṁ manamoldu pē<app><lem>ḻda</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḷde</rdg></app>na</l>
	  <l>nvitamati nāgavarmakavi śōdhisidar sale vādirājapaṁ</l>
	  <l>ḍitarene meccadippa khaḷanuṁ dorekoḷgume kēḷdoḍintidaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="22" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>kavitāguṇōdayaṁ vā</l>
	  <l>kyavinōdaṁ budhasarōjinīvanahaṁsaṁ</l>
	  <l>kavikarṇapūranē<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> nā</l>
	  <l>gavarmanu<app><lem>rvī vi</lem><rdg wit="#M">rvi</rdg></app>bhāgadoḷ sa<app><lem>le</lem><rdg wit="#M">ma</rdg></app> negaḻdaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="23" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>janakaṁ viprakuḷapradīpananaghaṁ dāmōdaraṁ petta tāy</l>
	  <l>vinayāḷaṅkr̥te vīrakabbe vara<app><lem>ṇaṁ </lem><rdg wit="#M">naṁ</rdg></app> śrīvīrabhaṭṭārakaṁ</l>
	  <l>tanayaṁ sadguṇamaṇḍanaṁ madhu valaṁ tānendoḍādoṁ<app><lem>du</lem><rdg wit="#M">da</rdg></app> sai</l>
	  <l>pina mānōnnatigintu nōnta naranārī nāgavarmambaraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="24" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>sahajakavi nāgavarmana</l>
	  <l>sahajaṁ kavi gamaki vādi vāgmitvaguṇaṁ</l>
	  <l>sahajaṁ tanagadu parama<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app></l>
	  <l>sahajanatāvaryanenisidaṁ nākāryaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="25" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l><note>idē padya alpa badalāvaṇeyoḍane kāvyāvalōkanada 497neya padyavāgi bandide.</note>sāravicāra cañcuramatiprasaraṁ paripakvaśāstrasaṁ</l>
	  <l>skāra<app><lem>nu</lem><rdg wit="#M">ma</rdg></app>pētakautukakaraṁ viditāgamalōkavr̥ttanu</l>
	  <l>tsāritamatsaraṁ sahajavatsaḷanelliyumītanendu ke</l>
	  <l>yvārade baṇṇikuṁ vasumatīvaḷayaṁ kavikarṇapūranaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="26" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>bigi pugidaḍamardu bagegese</l>
	  <l>va gadyaviracanege bāṇani<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>daṁ baṇṇaṁ</l>
	  <l>niguṇaṅgaṁ niguṇaṁ vr̥</l>
	  <l>ttaguṇaṁ pade<app><lem>de</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>ḍege nāgavarmakavīndraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="8"/>
	<lg n="27" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l>kannaḍadoḷ nega<app><lem>ḻte</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>yasagaṁ gajagaṁ guṇanandi ponnaneṁ</l>
	  <l>bannane saṁskr̥tōktige mayūrana bāṇana kāḷidāsanō</l>
	  <l>rannane bēṟe mattineṟigabbigarōḷigaroḷ poṇarce pē</l>
	  <l>ḻdannane balmevetta kavitādvayadoḷ kavitāguṇōdayaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="28" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>kavitāguṇakāñcananī</l>
	  <l>kavi mikka grāvanadhigatāmaḷabhāvaṁ</l>
	  <l>pravara guṇaratnavāridhi</l>
	  <l>vivēkanidhi nāgavarmanapagataśarmaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="29" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>oḍavuṭṭidudaṟitakkada</l>
	  <l>moḍanāḍidudoḍane tiḷivu baḷedudu geḍegoṁ</l>
	  <l>ḍoḍanōdidaḷ sarasvati</l>
	  <l>ga<app><lem>ḍi</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḷi</rdg></app>vinituṁ praṇidhi sukaviratnākaranā</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="30" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l><note>idē padya kāvyāvalōkanada 843neya padyavāgi bandide. ī padyadalli kāvyāvalōkana pāṭhagaḷannu mēliṭṭukoḷḷalāgide.</note>dhareyentante <app><lem>rasā</lem><rdg wit="#M">daśā</rdg></app>śrayaṁ jaḷadhiyentantātta gāmbhīrya<app><lem>maṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">dim</rdg></app></l>
	  <l><app><lem>ba</lem><rdg wit="#M">bha</rdg></app>ramentante sadāvr̥taṁ desega<app><lem>ḷen</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḍaṁ</rdg></app>tantūrjitaṁ sanda maṁ</l>
	  <l>daramentante suvarṇabhāsi śaśiyentaṁ<app><lem>tu</lem><rdg wit="#M">ma</rdg></app>jvaḷōdyat kaḷā</l>
	  <l>sphuritaṁ bhāvise nāgavarmaracitōdātta prabandhānvayaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="31" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>purupuṇyaṁ vimaḷōrukīrti sumati śrīnandanaṁ dharmasa</l>
	  <l>ccarita<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> vīrananantakāntiniḷayaṁ candraprabhāsyaṁ manō</l>
	  <l>harapārśvaṁ varapuṣpadantarajitaṁ śrēyōmataṁ suvrataṁ</l>
	  <l>dhareyoḷ tōrkurutarkikaṁ jinakumārābhāsamaṁ nākigaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="32" met="mālini">
	  <l>ji<app><lem>na</lem><rdg wit="#M">ta</rdg></app>matavanahaṁsaṁ vipravaṁśāvataṁsaṁ</l>
	  <l>jananuta guṇadhāmaṁ saccaritrābhirāmaṁ</l>
	  <l>vinayanayanidhānaṁ nissahāyāvadhānaṁ</l>
	  <l>svanugata śubhaśarmaṁ nirmaḷaṁ nāgavarmaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="9"/>
	<lg n="33" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>emba negaḻte jasakkā</l>
	  <l>ḷambanamāgire vinēyajanamaḻkaṟoḷā</l>
	  <l>daṁ bayasi kēḷe pēḻa</l>
	  <l>lkāṁ bagedeṁ vīranāthacaritāgamamaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="34" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>asadr̥śa vāgvibhūtiyutanādikavīśvaranindrabhūti va</l>
	  <l>rṇisida mahāpurāṇa katheyaṁ bhuvanatritaya prasiddhamaṁ</l>
	  <l>posayisi pēḻalī kr̥tiyoḷāṁ bagedeṁ bharadindamīsalā</l>
	  <l>ṭisuveḷavāḻeyantire timiṅgiḷanīsidagādha vārdhiyaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="35" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>idu bahutara puṇyāsrava</l>
	  <l>midu tattvaruci pramada<app><lem>da</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> sampatkaramiṁ</l>
	  <l>tidu saṁvēga samr̥ddhi</l>
	  <l>pradamondidanodavidartiyiṁ viracisuveṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="36" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>śrīvīracaritamaṁ pu</l>
	  <l>ṇyāvahamaṁ duritaharaṇakāraṇamaṁ bha</l>
	  <l>vyāvaḷi kēḷge samatvī</l>
	  <l>bhāvadinerdevuge vidagdha karṇāmr̥tamaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="37" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>mikkavaṟoḷēmo</l>
	  <l>ḷpokkire bhāvisuva sukr̥tiyoḷe tā</l>
	  <l>nakkuṁ tiḷivantāge ja</l>
	  <l>lakkane dharmārthakāmamōkṣādigaḷaṁ (?)</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>adentendoḍakhiḷa jaḷakarimakara timi timiṅgiḷagrāha nivaha saṁrambha<lb break="no"
	/>kṣōbhaṇādīrṇaraṅgattaraṅga bhaṅgurataraṅgamāḷākīrṇa lavaṇavāridhi parikṣipta<lb break="no"
