	/>nijaśarīrabhāramaniḻipi śatārakalpadoḷ sāmānikadēvanādoṁ tatparōkṣa<lb break="no"
	/>doḷ viśvanandi mumukṣugaḷēkavihāratvamanettikoṇḍu</p>
	<lg n="43" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l>grāmadoḷantadondu dinamaṁ nagaraṅgaḷoḷaidahaṅgaḷaṁ</l>
	  <l>bhīmamahāṭavī nikaṭadoḷ daśarātramanāgamōktiyiṁ</l>
	  <l>tāmirutaṁ kramakramadinā munipuṅgavareydevandaru</l>
	  <l>ddāma vinūtacūtavanakāntamanā madhurāpurāntamaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu bandā purada bahirudyānabhūmiyoḷamanēka śākhānikāya<lb break="no"
	/>kamanīyamappa sahakāra bhūruhada modaloḷirdativiśāḷa śikhāpaṭṭakada mēle <lb
	/>panthāticāra niyamaṅgeydu kiṟidupottu viśramisi madhyāhnavēḷeyoḷ <lb
	/>caryāmārgadiṁ poḻalaṁ pokku rathyāmārgambiḍidu bappudumalli</p>
	<lg n="44" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>eni<app><lem>suṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">suvu</rdg></app>māṇade gōvugaḷ taguḷe keṅgōlnantaḍumaṁ biṭṭu mumbī (?)</l>
	  <l>ḍinoḷārirdoḍamaṭṭi pāydiṟivutaṁ barpāvu meyverci bhōṁ</l>
	  <l>kene caryāgata viśvanandimuniyaṁ kaṇḍeyde pottetti kō</l>
	  <l>ḍinoḷīḍāḍuvuduṁ siḍildu neladoḷ birdaṁ munīndrōttamaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="29"/>
	<p><label>va.</label>aṁ<app><lem>ta</lem><rdg wit="#M">tani</rdg></app>bhrāśanighātadinduruḷdu keḍeda permaradante neladoḷ <lb
	/>birdiṟiyaladaṟa prakāṇḍanaṁ kaṇḍu guṇḍu gaḍaṇaṅgoṇḍu taṇḍataṇḍadiṁ <lb
	/>nōḍuttamirpudumā prastāvadoḷ munne pēḻda viśākhanandi kāmarū<lb break="no"
	/>pādhipatiyiṁ parōbhūtanāgi nāḍuṁ bīḍumumaṁ sōltu seṟegevandu <lb
	/>lēkhavāhakavr̥ttiyaṁ pūṇdu biḍisikoṇḍu naḍeyuttaṁ tadādēśadindamuttara<lb break="no"
	/>madhurāpurādhināyakaṅge saṁvāhadole<app><lem>yaṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">yuṁ</rdg></app> pāvuḍamaṁ koṇḍubandu</p>
	<lg n="45" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>uḍedōluṁ paṇekaṭṭuṁ</l>
	  <l>maḍamēṟisi meṭṭidekkavaḍamuṁ keyyoḷ</l>
	  <l>piḍidirda kuñcamuṁ tana</l>
	  <l>goḍambaḍaṁoḍeye lēkhavāhākr̥tiyoḷ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>ā poḻala bīdibīdiyoḷ toḻaluttaṁ bappātaṁ munde musuṟi <lb
	/>neṟedunindu nōḻpa neraviyaṁ kaṇḍidēnendeydevandu bhāvisinōḍi basida<lb break="no"
	/>dasiyantappa pasuvina kōḻkaḷerdeyanucci basavaḷidu nondu birdirda <lb
	/>muniyaṁ kaṇḍu viśvanandiyappudanaṟidu manadoḷāda kāypaṁ keygāya<lb break="no"
	/>lāṟade sarandōṟi mundenindu</p>
	<lg n="46" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>āvaṟi<app><lem>yal</lem><rdg wit="#M">ya</rdg></app> munne nīnu</l>
	  <l><app><lem>māva</lem><rdg wit="#M">dyāna</rdg></app> bhujābaḷamamānuṣaṁ baḍapaṭṭoṁ</l>
	  <l>dāviṟiye keḍedu bīdiyo</l>
	  <l>ḷāvaḍivaḍuvudumadīgaḷādude ninagaṁ (?)</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="47" met="mahāsragdhare">
	  <l><note>idu kāvyāvalōkanada 364neya padyavāgi bandide.</note>munisiṁ mēle<app><lem>rdu</lem><rdg source="#kāvya">tti</rdg></app>barpandina vipuḷa śiḷāstambhamaṁ kīṟi kīḻvaṁ</l>
	  <l>dina beṅkoṇḍaṭṭi<app><lem>gelvaṁ</lem><rdg source="#kāvya">kolvaṁ</rdg></app>dina tiripi kapitthāvanījātadindaṁ</l>
	  <l>banadoḷ me<app><lem>yviṭṭu</lem><rdg source="#kāvyā">yverci</rdg></app> poyvandina nijabhujavikrāntamēnādudintī</l>
	  <l>janamellaṁ nōḍe cauvaṭṭada bisu<app><lem>vu</lem><rdg wit="#M">ha</rdg></app>ḍiyoḷ birdu sāvaṁ tuṭāytē</l>
	  <l></l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>endu neṟananetti mūdalisuttamā puruṣādhamana nuḍida mātiṅge <lb
	/>mahāmuni munidu munida kōpa<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> manōdurlabhaṁ embudaṁ nannimāḍi <pb n="30"
	/>manadoḷ kalaṅki kaluṣāviḷaṅgaḷappa kaṇgaḷaṁ teṟedu nandida viśākhanandiyaṁ <lb
	/>toṭṭane kaṇḍu kaḍupinoḷ pudugi <app><lem>kiḍi ki</lem><rdg wit="#M">kaṇḍigi</rdg></app>ḍiyāgi ninnaninnelli puṭṭidoḍaṁ <lb
	/>kolladirenendu tadhvajayānadānamaṁ nidhānaṅgeydu</p>
	<lg n="48" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>ā viśvanandimuni saṁ</l>
	  <l>bhāvitatattvaṁ tadīya virasōktigaḷiṁ</l>
	  <l>dēvaṁ pudidire muni saṁ</l>
	  <l>bhāvisi kaḷedaṁ nijāsuvaṁ nisuvindaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā munīśvaranasuvaṁ visarjisi viśākhabhūti puṭṭida śatārakalpa<lb break="no"
	/>doḷ sāmānikadēvanāgi puṭṭi</p>
	<lg n="49" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l>bāḍada puṣpamāle nijadindoḍavuṭṭida bhūṣaṇaṁ rati</l>
	  <l>krīḍeyanāgaḷuṁ salisutippamarījanamādamaḻkaṟaṁ</l>
	  <l>māḍuvinaṁ sukhāmbunidhiyoḷ manamoldanurāgadiṁ<app><lem>da</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>mō</l>
	  <l>lāḍidanīḍitaśvatanukāntiyutaṁ guṇaratnasāgaraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="50" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>tridaśastrīparigīta kīrtiruci maccandrāvabhāsaṁ virā</l>
	  <l>jada mānōjvaḷa nūtnaratnamakuṭaṁ sampadyamānōtsavā</l>
	  <l>bhyudayaṁ nirjitarōgaśōkanodavaṁ tāḷdirdanānandadiṁ</l>
	  <l>padineṇṭambudhigaḷvaraṁ sukhadoḷā samyaktvaratnākaraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<trailer><label>gadya</label>idu sakaḷa sukavijanamanassarōjinīrājahaṁsāyamāna<lb
	/>mānānūna kavitāguṇōdayaṁ śrīmannāgavarma viracitamappa<lb
	/>śrīvīra vardhamānapurāṇadoḷ<lb
	/>dvitīyāśvāsaṁ</trailer>
      </div>
      <div n="3" type="āśvāsaṁ">
	<pb n="31"/>
	<head>tr̥tīyāśvāsaṁ</head>
	<lg n="1" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l>ittaludātta bhāratamahītaḷadoḷ paripālipa nr̥saṁ</l>
	  <l>pattige janmabhūmi sakaḷartuphaḷakke vipākalōkama</l>
	  <l>tyuttama puṇyabhājanajanakke sabhājanamemba meyme me</l>
	  <l>yvettire rañjikuṁ janapadaṁ dorevetta suramyanāmadiṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="2" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>dharaṇīmukhābjamenisuva</l>
	  <l>suramya<app><lem>ke</lem><rdg wit="#M">kke</rdg></app> mogakke mūgu tānembantā</l>
	  <l>gire sogayisuvudu paudana</l>
	  <l>puraṁ samuttuṅga ramyaharmyaprakaraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="3" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>adanadaṭaṁ prajāpatimahīpatiyāḷvanaśēṣa maṅgaḷā</l>
	  <l>bhyudayaparamparā parigatōdayanā nr̥pakuñjarakke bē</l>
	  <l>ṭada satiyar jayāvatiyumā mr̥gabhūvatiyembaḷuṁ samu</l>
	  <l>nmada vanadanti<app><lem>giṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">diṁ</rdg></app>tiveraḍuṁ madalēkhegaḷemba māḻkeyiṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antavaroḷā  mahānubhāvanēkībhāvadiṁ saṁsārasukhamaṁ <lb
	/>kaḍeyāgadanteyanubhavisi</p>
	<lg n="4" met="rathōddhataṁ">
	  <l>ā jayāvatige puṭṭidaṁ mahā</l>
	  <l>rājavaibhavapadōcitaṁ sutaṁ</l>
	  <l>tējamunnati<app><lem>keyuṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">yaṁ</rdg></app> parākramaṁ</l>
	  <l>sājamāge vijayākhyanāmadiṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="32"/>
	<lg n="5" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>lōkaṁ guḍigaṭṭe mr̥gā</l>
	  <l>ḷōke mr̥ga <app><lem>ya</lem><rdg wit="#M">yā</rdg></app>vatige  puṭṭidaṁ tanayaṁ ni</l>
	  <l>rvyākuḷa śauryaṁ bhuvana</l>
	  <l>vyā<app><lem>kr̥</lem><rdg wit="#M">vr̥</rdg></app>tayaśanatibaḷaṁ tripiṣṭakumāraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu viśākhabhūticaranappa sā sāmānikaṁ bandu vijayanemba <lb
	/>baladēvanāgiyuṁ viśvanandicaranappa dēvaṁ bandu tripiṣṭanembanemba prathamavāsu <lb
	/>dēvanāgiyumavarge puṭṭa janmāntarānugata sahajasnēhadindondidorva<lb break="no"
	/>rorvaroḷeccaḍaḻkaṟuṁ kūrmeyumadhikamāgi baḷeye</p>
	<lg n="6" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>gurubhujagarvamarvisuva tējadagu<app><lem>rvu</lem><rdg wit="#M">rva</rdg></app>  nayāgamakramaṁ</l>
	  <l>parijinoḷondi ninda kaḍugāḍi podaḻdesevoḷguṇaṁ para</l>
	  <l>sparamanurūpamāge karamoppidarirvarumorvarorvaroḷ</l>
	  <l>sarigoḷe pāṭi pāsaṭi samaṁ sarisaṅgoḷe pōlveyembinaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā kumāradvayamaśēṣa lōkābhyarthitārthapratāna nidhāna<lb break="no"
	/>kalpavr̥kṣāṅkuravaḷayaṁ baḷevantoḍane baḷedu navayavvanaprāptarāge</p>
	<lg n="7" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>atiśayabhadralakṣaṇanudagrataraṁ madhupiṅganētranu</l>
	  <l>nnataśiranudghamēghaninadaṁ parighāyata bāhudaṇḍana</l>
	  <l>nvita vinayāmbujātadaśanaṁ sa satatōrjitadānanabhramū</l>
	  <l>patiyavoloppidaṁ himaghanapratibhāsi mahābaḷaṁ baḷaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="8" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>daḷita dhavaḷābja muktā</l>
	  <l>phaḷa śaṅkha śaśāṅka nikāśa  <app><lem>su</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>vini</l>
	  <l>rmaḷa ruciravarṇanuṁ sale</l>
	  <l>taḷedaṁ haḷi tanna meyyoḷaṁ lōkadoḷaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="9" met="trividhi">
	  <l>baḷanēkakuṇḍaḷaṁ baḷi tāḷakētanaṁ</l>
	  <l>haḷahasta nīḷavahanaṁ saṅkarṣaṇaṁ</l>
	  <l>baḷabhadraṁ rāmanene sandaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="33"/>
	<lg n="10" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>bageyalagamyamunnati manaṅgoḷa<app><lem>la</lem><rdg wit="#M">lu</rdg></app> ttaḷagaṁ parākramaṁ</l>
	  <l>negaḻalagōcaraṁ caritamīkṣisalaccari rūpu vibhramaṁ</l>
	  <l>pogaḻalaḷumbamoḷpeṇisalatyadhikaṁ guṇamendu koṇḍu nā</l>
	  <l>lageyavarennaruṁ neṟeye baṇṇisalār nerevar tripiṣṭanaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="11" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>beralanukūḷa mitrajanadante susaṅgatamāptamantriyaṁ</l>
	  <l>tire ruciraṁ nakhāvaḷi taḷaṁ taḷadantanurāgarañjitaṁ</l>
	  <l>paredu nijaprayuktacararante nigūḍhamenippa pempanā</l>
	  <l>varisi manakkevandesegumaṅghriyugaṁ sarasīruhākṣanā</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="12" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>śumbhāspada vipuḷataḷa</l>
	  <l>stambhaṁ tamagamare vikramaprāsāda</l>
	  <l>stambhamivene karamesevuvu</l>
	  <l>rambhāsthambhāyamānamūrustambhaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="13" met="utpalamālike">
	  <l>bhāsurahēmapatra kaṭisūtra pariṣkr̥tamādirājya siṁ</l>
	  <l>hāsana yōgyamintidene nirjita viśruta hastimastakō</l>
	  <l>llāsamanaṅgarāgarasapūra sunirbhara sētubandhanaṁ</l>
	  <l>māsaramoppi tōṟuvudu siṁhakaṭītaṭamā nr̥siṁhanā</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="14" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>ghanakānti samuttuṅgaṁ</l>
	  <l>sanābhi baḷisaṁyutaṁ lasat padmāṅkaṁ</l>
	  <l>vanajōdaranudaramadā</l>
	  <l>tana teṟanane pōltu dhanamaniradeṟagisuguṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="15" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>lalitavicitrabhitti hr̥dayapravikāśavibhāsi gōminī</l>
	  <l>kuḷagr̥hamembinaṁ bagegevappudadikke nijāṅgakasthaḷa</l>
	  <l>sthaḷaparilambamānana mahārasa<app><lem>mā</lem><rdg wit="#M">mupā</rdg></app>hita patrabhaṅgamu</l>
	  <l>jvaḷa maṇitōraṇaṅgaḷene kaṇgeseguṁ bhujadaṇḍamātanā</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="34"/>
	<lg n="16" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>hāramupakaṇṭhadēśado</l>
	  <l>ḷōrantamardire mukhēndubimbakke śara</l>
	  <l><app><lem>ttā</lem><rdg wit="#M">tkā</rdg></app>rāḷiśaṅke bagevaṁ</l>
	  <l>tāra manakkaṁ jalakkanudayisi tōrkuṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="17" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>anudīrṇasphuraduttarādharadaḷaṁ susnigdhadantāṁśu bhū</l>
	  <l>tana satkēsararājitaṁ smitavikāsōllāsamucchēdyamā</l>
	  <l>na navasmaśrukaḷāpasampa<app><lem>da madāḷi</lem><rdg wit="#M">tadaḷi</rdg></app>śrēṇitaṁ muñjikē</l>
	  <l>śana vaktrāmbujamembinaṁ sogayikuṁ vāgdēvatādhiṣṭhitaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="18" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>surabhisamucchvāsāniḷa</l>
	  <l>parimaḷamati nibiḍapuṭanudagraṁ nīḷāṁ</l>
	  <l>buruhada mukuḷamaninisanu</l>
	  <l>kari<app><lem>sida</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>pudu śārṅgadharana nāsāvaṁśaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="19" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>śrutaśāstrōpanayaṅgaḷeyde r̥jugaḷ vr̥ddhōpamānaṅgaḷī</l>
	  <l>śrutigaḷ nikkuvamendu sārda nayadiṁ meyvetta varṇatraya</l>
	  <l>sthitayaṁ pāḷisidantaḷiśrita samudyatkētakāntar daḷā</l>
	  <l>kr̥ti raktāyata rājilōcanayugaṁ tatpuṇḍarīkākṣanā</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="20" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>maṟasidanennaṁ kaṇḍaṟi</l>
	  <l><app><lem>duṟa</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>dire bilvalme tanna meyyoḷadakkī</l>
	  <l>poṟeyēvudendanaṅgaṁ</l>
	  <l>muṟidirikida billaniḷisuguṁ bhrūyugaḷaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="21" met="mahāsragdhare">
	  <l>caturambhōrāśivēḷāvr̥ta sakaḷamahīmaṇḍaḷaṁ dōrva<app><lem>ḷā</lem><rdg wit="#M">rā</rdg></app>sā</l>
	  <l>ditamēkacchatramintī vibhugenisuvavol saṅgatōṣita vibhrā (?)</l>
	  <l>jitamā nīḷāḷakāḷīkr̥ta makuṭa haṭa<app><lem>jjū</lem><rdg wit="#M">jū</rdg></app>ṭakaṁ chatradondā</l>
	  <l>kr̥tiyaṁ tānāntu kaṇgoppugumavana samuttuṅgamūrdhvapradēśaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antanupamāna rūpaguṇasampattigaṁ yauvanōdāttavr̥ttigaṁ <lb
	/>neleyāgi bhōgadoḷ mahēndrana<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> tējapratāpadoḷagnidēvananājñā<lb break="no"
	/>vidhānadoḷ daṇḍadharanaṁ bhīṣaṇaprakr̥tiyoḷ nilisiyuṁ sarvasattva<pb break="no" n="35"
	/>sāmyateyoḷ varuṇanuma<app><lem>nu</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>dagra baḷadoḷaniḷanaṁ dā<app><lem>nadākhyāyi</lem><rdg wit="#M">nidākhyāmbu</rdg></app>ke<lb break="no"
	/>yoḷ kubērananaiśvaryadodavi<app><lem>no</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>ḷīśā<app><lem>na</lem><rdg wit="#M">śa</rdg></app>naṁ pōltu sakaḷa lōka<lb break="no"
	/>pāḷānubhāvamaṁ tannoḷ taḷedu bhuvanarakṣādhikāramanappukeydu</p>
	<lg n="22" met="mahāsragdhare">
	  <l>aṇamāruṁ sāralaṇmar pesargoḷe desegeṭṭōḍuvar<app><lem>tānumī</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>dhā</l>
	  <l>riṇiyaṁ tanniccheyindindaṇivi<app><lem>ṇi</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>geyu<app><lem>ti</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>rdappudendintidaṁ kē</l>
	  <l>ḷdaṇabāraṁ pecce pokkappaḷisi piḍidu pēsēḻe sīḷdikkidaṁ bhī</l>
	  <l>ṣaṇa māyāvēṣamaṁ kēsariyanasama vikrāntadindaṁ tripiṣṭaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="23" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>poccumbōgada śauryama</l>
	  <l>daccariyāgire mr̥gāriyaṁ po<app><lem>kka</lem><rdg wit="#M">kkaṇarda</rdg></app>ḻaliṁ</l>
	  <l>maccarisi kondu nacciṁ</l>
	  <l>mecce jagaṁ taguḷe pogaḻe negaḻdaṁ kr̥ṣṇaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>mattorme narmasaciva pradhāna prakr̥tipuruṣapravēka parivr̥taṁ <lb
	/>prajāpatimahārājanāsthānabhūmiyoḷippuduṁ vasantanembonaṣṭāṅga nimitta<lb break="no"
	/>vittaṁ naimittakaṁ bandu nimma kiṟiyamaganī puruṣōttamaṁ tripiṣṭaṁ <lb
	/>trikhaṇḍamaṇḍaḷādhipanamōghanakkumadakkaṁ kōṭikaśiḷāsamuddharaṇaṁ pratyaya<lb break="no"
	/>mendaṟiye pēḻdu sabhāsadara sannidhānadoḷādēśapatramaṁ kuḍuvudamarasanati<lb break="no"
	/>sambhramākrāntasvāntanāgi rāgisi daivajñanannādaramberasu mannisi kaḷipi <lb
	/>katipayadinaṅgaḷi<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> nāmamudbhūtamaṁ nōḻpa kautūhaḷadiṁ vijayanuṁ <lb
	/>tripiṣṭanuṁ berasanēka rājakumāraparivēṣṭitaṁ kōṭikaseleyaṁ muṭṭevandu</p>
	<lg n="24" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>aḷavaṁ sabhyata nr̥pasura</l>
	  <l>roḷarappaḍe nōḻpamī mahāśileyaṁ dō</l>
	  <l>rvaḷadindettuvudene saṁ</l>
	  <l>caḷisade pūṇdettidaṁ baḷasthaṁ  kr̥ṣṇaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="25" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>aṟikeya kōṭikaśileyaṁ</l>
	  <l>taṟisanduṟadetti pottu māṇdane lōkaṁ</l>
	  <l>bēṟāgi kīrtisuttire</l>
	  <l>tiṟikallāḍidanadaṁ tripiṣṭakumāraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="36"/>
	<p><label>va.</label>antananyasāmānyamappa sāścaryaśauryamuṁ bāhuvīrya<lb break="no"
	/>mumaṁ neṟedu sukhamirpannegamattaṁ</p>
	<lg n="26" met="sundaraṁ">
