	  <l>śrēṇiyoḷuṇṭu mahāpuraṁ rathanūpuraṁ</l>
	  <l>śōṇamaṇipravirājita pratikarma ni</l>
	  <l>rmāṇa vicitra viśāḷa<app><lem>ḷō</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḷā</rdg></app>hina gōpuraṁ</l>
