	  <l>rpavaḷaṅgōjvaḷakāntigantavaḷa lāvaṇyakke bappannaḷā</l>
	  <l>divajastrīyaroḷambarēcarasatī sandōhadoḷpaṁ nagēṁ</l>
	  <l>dravadhūvr̥ndadoḷilla pōlvegene mattēvaṇṇipaṁ baṇṇipaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="37"/>
	<lg n="31" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>rucira navakusuma parikara</l>
	  <l>nicitaṁ bāḷapravāḷajāḷamidene tat</l>
