	<p><label>va.</label>antā dvijānvayanaṟivuṁ vinayamuṁ tannoḍavuṭṭe puṭṭi baḷedu <lb
	/>pūrvasthitiyoḷe maskarimārgadoḷesagi matta<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> māhēndrakalpadoḷ dēva<lb break="no"
