	<lg n="21" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>eneyene tanna munnina bhavaṅgaḷa saṅgatiyellamāvagaṁ</l>
	  <l>kanasina māḻkeyiṁ manadoḷāgire cāraṇapādamūladoḷ</l>
	  <l>vinayadinerdu nirgaḷi<app><lem>tada</lem><rdg wit="#M">tā</rdg></app>śrujalaṅgaḷinarghyapādyamaṁ</l>
