	  <l>pāḷaṅge nagēndrasāra vastūtkaramaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā vyantarāmaranarasanaṁ kaṇḍu cakravartiyukta sanmānāmr̥ta<lb break="no"
	/>svādadiṁ santuṣṭanāgi pōge mattamā mahīdhara<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>taṭambiḍidu bīḍuviḍuttaṁ <lb
	/>mūḍamogade naḍedu raktānadīkaṇṭhakkāgi bappuduṁ cakrādhīśana barevaneṟidu <lb
	/>parivāraparīteyāgi bandu kaṇḍu</p>
	<pb n="166"/>
	<lg n="64" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>vividhauṣadhi sambhr̥ta pu</l>
	  <l>ṇyavāriyiṁ tāne majjanambugisi mahō</l>
	  <l>tsavadinavaṭayisidaḷ ca</l>
	  <l>kravartiganurakte rakte siṁhāsanamaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu mahāvibhūtiyiṁ bandu kaṇḍa raktādēviyaṁ manaṁ <lb
	/>goṇḍarkaṟoḷ priyaṁ nuḍidirisi dakṣiṇapaścimāśāmukhanāgi caṭuḷa <lb
	/>prayāṇaṁ madhyamakhaṇḍada madhyapradēśamanaḷaṅkarisikoṇḍirdu vr̥ṣabhācaḷada <lb
	/>keladoḷāgi bīḍubiṭṭāgaḷ</p>
	<lg n="65" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>muṁ bhujavikramadiṁ vi</l>
	  <l>śvambhareyaṁ geldu negaḻda cakrigaḷa jaya</l>
	  <l>stambhamidene tōṟidudu</l>
	  <l>ttambhita surasaraṇi sanda vr̥ṣabhagirīndraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>ā girīndradoḷātmīya viśvaviśvambharātaḷa vijayayaśaḥpraśastiyaṁ <lb
	/>śāsanamāge bareyal bagedu mantri purōhita sēnāni pramukhapradhāna<lb break="no"
	/>puruṣaparivr̥taneydevandu baḷasiyuṁ to<app><lem>ḻaldu</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḷardu</rdg></app> nōḻpudumalli</p>
	<lg n="66" met="campakamāle">
	  <l>jagadoḷanādikāla parivartanadoḷ kaḻidādicakrava</l>
	  <l>rtigaḷa jayapraśastigaḷanōdisi kēḷdu taduktigaḷ manaṁ</l>
	  <l>buge bagedeydi mantrimanadantire bhāvisi nōḍe nōḍe to</l>
	  <l>ṭṭage paṟipaṭṭu pōdudu madajvara<app><lem>mā</lem><rdg wit="#M">hā</rdg></app> priyamitracakri<app><lem>yā</lem><rdg wit="#M">yaṁ</rdg></app></l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antatikrāntarāda sarvapārthivarappādirājara viśvatōdātta vaṁśa<lb break="no"
	/>vīrya śrutādi guṇavarṇanaśravaṇadiṁ vyapagatamadanāgi purātana cakravarti<lb break="no"
	/>mārgānuvr̥ttinimittadindidirameyyoḷondu praśastiyiṁ daṇḍaratnadiṁ toḍe<lb break="no"
	/>deḍemāḍi kākiṇīratnadindanēka nijanāmāṅkamāḷikāprapañca ravanāpurassaraṁ <lb
	/>ṣaṭkhaṇḍa pr̥thvīmaṇḍaḷa vijayōpalabdha yaśaḥpraśastiyaṁ bareyisi khaṇḍaprapāta<lb break="no"
	/>guhegaḷāgi taḷardu keladevasadiṁ vijayārdhamaneydi tadana<app><lem>ghēṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">gēṁ</rdg></app>draprastha<lb break="no"
	/>doḷavasthita vijayaśibiraṁ pūrvōktamārgadinā guhādvārada paḍiyaṁ <lb
	/>teṟedadaṟa beṅkeyāṟuvannegaṁ mūḍaṇadeseya mlēcchakhaṇḍamaṁ bāykēḷi <lb
	/>sendu sēnādhināthanaṁ besasi nelevīḍu māḍi nindāgaḷ</p>
	<pb n="167"/>
	<lg n="67" met="mālabhāriṇi">
	  <l><note>idakke vasantamālikā, aupacchandasika, subōdhitā, priyā emba hesarugaḷū ive.</note>abhayārthigaḷāgi bandu kaṇḍi</l>
	  <l>rdubhayaśrēṇiya khēcarādhirājar</l>
	  <l>śubhalakṣaṇalakṣitaṅgaḷaṁ taṁ</l>
	  <l>dibhavāhādigaḷaṁ nr̥paṅge koṭṭar</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>mattamatyanta rūpalāvaṇyaśīlaguṇasampanneyaṁ subhadreyemba <lb
	/>kanneyaṁ vivāhavidhiyiṁ koṭṭu bandhusambandhamumaṁ nr̥tyasambandhamuma<lb break="no"
	/>nuṇṭumāḍi cakravartiyaṁ bīḻkoṇḍu pōdarannegaṁ daṇḍanāyakaṁ prābhr̥<lb break="no"
	/>nmlēcchakhaṇḍamaṁ besekeysi vastuvāhanaṅgaḷaṁ kaige māḍi bappudumanantaramā <lb
	/>narēndracakravarti samastasādhanasahitamallindettikoṇḍa pratāpaguheyaṁ muṭṭe <lb
	/>vandu pūrvasthitiyinadaṟeraḍuṁ deseya kērgaḷoḷ kākiṇīratnōtkarṇaṁ <lb
	/>gaḷappa candrādityabimbaṅgaḷa beḷaginoḷamanēka makuṭabaddhakṣatriyakumāra maṇi<lb break="no"
	/>tirīṭaprabhāprasaradoḷaṁ cakraratnōdyōtamāna tējaḥprakāśadoḷaṁ nirā<lb break="no"
	/>kuḷaṁ maguḻdu dakṣiṇadvāradiṁ poṟamaḍuvāgaḷ</p>
	<lg n="68" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>bhr̥ṅgāradarpaṇapramu</l>
	  <l>khaṅgaḷ sukhamaṅgaḷōpakaraṇaṅgaḷ ce</l>
	  <l>lvaṁ geḍegoṇḍire bandu nr̥</l>
	  <l>paṅgidirgoṇḍeṟagi nāṭyamāḷaṁ kaṇḍaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu nāṭyamāḷāmaraṁ kanakāḷaṅkādi maṅgaḷōpakaraṇadravyā<lb break="no"
	/>rpaṇadiṁ manaṅgoṇḍu kaṇḍu cakravartige vaśavartiyāgi pōpuduṁ tadananta<lb break="no"
	/>ramā tāranagada tāradoḷe bīḍambiḍisi mūḍaṇa deseya mlēcchakhaṇḍadavargaṁ <lb
	/>sēnāpatiyanaṭṭi tannāṇeyuṁ ghōṣaṇeyuṁ naḍevantu sādhyaṁ māḍi siddha<lb break="no"
	/>siddhijayanādanintu</p>
	<lg n="69" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>uttarabharataṁ bāykē</l>
	  <l>ḷdarttu khagēndrāva<app><lem>nīvi</lem><rdg wit="#M">ni</rdg></app>bhāgaṁ bāykē</l>
	  <l>ḷdarttu surasamiti bāykē</l>
	  <l>ḷdarttene cakrige bigurpa maṇḍalamoḷavē</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="168"/>
	<lg n="70" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>dvādaśamaṇḍalamemba vi</l>
	  <l>bhēdaṁ priyamitra jaitrayātreyoḷadu tā</l>
	  <l>nādude kāṇalkade ta</l>
	  <l>kkādudu ṣaṭkhaṇḍamaṇḍitaṁ bhūtaḷamuṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā kr̥tātmaṁ karaṭīkr̥ta dikcakramaṁ viṣayīkr̥tāśēṣapārthi<lb break="no"
	/>vanuṁ nirākr̥ta nikhiḷalōkapāḷaprabhāvanu<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> mahīkr̥ta pratyantana<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> dūrī<lb break="no"
	/>kr̥tārātigōtranuṁ prakāśīkr̥ta bhujapratāpanumaṅgīkr̥ta sārvabhauma<lb break="no"
	/>sāmrājyanuṁ pūrīkr̥ta mahaiśvaryanumātmīkr̥ta mahānubhāvanumadharī<lb break="no"
	/>kr̥tamahēndraviḷāsanuṁ hastakr̥ta daśāṅgabhōganu<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> svādūkr̥ta saṁsāra<lb break="no"
	/>saukhyanumāgi nirvartitāśēṣabhuvanavijayanātmīyarājadhānige puṇḍarīkiṇige <lb
	/>maguḻdu kelavu divasadinaprayāsadoḷeydevandu</p>
	<lg n="71" met="mahāsragdhare">
	  <l>karisēnācakra ghaṇṭāninada badhiritāśāntaraṁ valgavalga</l>
	  <l>tturagānīka sphuṭōdyatkr̥ta <app><lem>khura</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app>śikharōtkampitakṣōṇibhāgaṁ</l>
	  <l>taruṇārka svaprakāśōjvaḷatara rucirōccakrabhābhāsyamānāṁ</l>
	  <l>baracakraṁ bandu pokkaṁ nijapuravaramaṁ rāgadiṁ sārvabhaumaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu ṣaṭkhaṇḍāvanīmaṇḍaḷavibhāgamaneyde bāykēḷisi nijā<lb break="no"
	/>nvayarājadhāni samāniṣṭhitānuttarōttara siṁhāsanāsīnanāgi</p>
	<lg n="72" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>besanaṁ pārdire māgadhādyakhiḷa vānavyantarādhīśvarar</l>
	  <l>masakaṅgundi śaraṇge vandire khagakṣōṇībhujar vikrama</l>
	  <l>prasarakkaḷkire vairimaṇḍaḷikarurvīcakramaṁ kūḍe pā</l>
	  <l>ḷisidaṁ kṣatraguṇaṁ<app><lem>manaṅgoḷipinaṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">goḷpinaṁ</rdg></app> samyaktvaratnākaraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<trailer><label>gadya</label>idu nikhiḷa sukavijana manassarōjinīvanahaṁsāyamāna mānānūna<lb
	/>kavitāguṇōdaya śrīmannāgavarma viracitamappa śrivīravardhamāna<lb
	/>purāṇadoḷ cakravarti ṣaṭkhaṇḍamaṇḍaḷavijayavarṇana<app><lem>ṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app><lb
	/>namamāśvāsaṁ</trailer>
