      <div n="10" type="āśvāsaṁ">
	<pb n="169"/>
	<head>daśamāśvāsaṁ</head>
	<lg n="1" met="śārdūlavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>śrīnārīpati nissapatnavibhavaṁ tīvrapratāpaṁ padā</l>
	  <l>bjānamnāvanipāḷavauḷighaṭita prōttuṅgavīthītaṭaṁ</l>
	  <l>pīnaprāṁśu bhujāvasasthi vijayaśrīkāmukaṁ dattalō</l>
	  <l>kānandaṁ nayadindamāḷdaneḷeyaṁ saumitrabhūvallabhaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="2" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>maravembude surataruvaṁ</l>
	  <l>paralembude negaḻe negaḻda cintāmaṇiyaṁ</l>
	  <l>naranembude bhūbhuvanē</l>
	  <l>śvaranaṁ nirupamaguṇaprabhāvada kaṇiyaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<lg n="3" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>aṟanaṁ nirmaḷavr̥ttidānadodavaṁ sampatti<app><lem>sau</lem><rdg wit="#M">sa</rdg></app>myōktiyoḷ</l>
	  <l>neṟedoḷpaṁ nutavāgmitāguṇamatikṣāntiyiṁ śauryameṁ (?)</l>
	  <l>daṟi<app><lem>veṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">meṁ</rdg></app>dintinitaṁ guṇāntaramanāvondirpa<app><lem>meṁ</lem><rdg wit="#M">moṁ</rdg></app>dande pēḻ</l>
	  <l>peṟanāvaṁ doregembinaṁ negaḻdanā viśvambharāvallabhaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā mahābhāgadhēyanamēyaguṇamaṇiprarōhaṇanāgi diva<lb break="no"
	/>sakara sahasraprabhāpratānamanaggalisi pajjaḷisi beḷaguva sudarśanamemba cakra<lb break="no"
	/>ratnamuṁ saunandakamemba kaukṣēyakamuṁ caṇḍavēgamemba daṇḍaratnamuṁ <lb
	/>sūryaprabhamembātapatramuṁ cūḍāmaṇiyemba maṇiyuṁ cintājanani<lb break="no"
	/>yemba kākiṇīratnamuṁ vajramayamemba carmaratnamuṁ manōvēganemba <lb
	/>sēnāpatiyuṁ buddhisāgaranemba purōhitanuṁ kāmavr̥ṣṭiyemba bhaṇḍāri<lb break="no"
	/>ganuṁ bhadramukhanemba sthapatiyuṁ vijayaparvatamemba yāgahastiyuṁ pava<lb break="no"
	/>nañjayamemba turagaratnamuṁ subhadreyemba strīratnamumintī padinālkuṁ <lb
	/>jīvājīvaratnaṅgaḷ mattaṁ samucitōpabhōgadravyaṅgaḷaṁ kuḍuva kāḷa<lb break="no"
	/>nidhiyuṁ nānā prasāda bhōjanōpakaraṇaṅgaḷanīva mahākāḷamuṁ divya<pb break="no" n="170"
	/>śayyāsana prabhēdaṅgaḷaṁ paḍeva naisarpamuṁ śāḷivrīhyādi dhānyō<app><lem>pa</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app><lb break="no"
	/>sarpanāśravaṇamappa pāṇḍuvuṁ kṣōma kaukṣēyakādi śastraviśēṣa pradāyi<lb break="no"
	/>yappa padmanidhiyuṁ maṇimayavicitra bhūṣaṇāvitaraṇaṅgeyva piṅgaḷamemba <lb
	/>ratnamuṁ śakti<app><lem>bhū</lem><rdg wit="#M">bhā</rdg></app>ṣaṇamadamantapramukha vividhāyudhaṅgaḷanoḷagoṇḍirpa <lb
	/>māṇavakamumātōdyahr̥dyavādyaṅgaḷaṁ janiyisuva śaṅkhanidhiyuṁ kanaka<lb break="no"
	/>maṇimuktādi nānā vastuvaṁ kuḍuva bhārōṣanicitamappa sarvaratnamumeṁ <lb
	/><app><lem>bomba</lem><rdg wit="#M">bo</rdg></app>ttuṁ mahānidhigaḷuṁ mūvatticchāsira nirantara saṅgītaprasaṅgasaṅga<lb break="no"
	/>tōttuṅga nāṭyaśālegaḷuṁ mūvatticchāsirvarubhayakula viśuddhakṣatriyarappa <lb
	/>kulavadhūjanamuṁ mūvatticchāsirva<app><lem>r</lem><rdg wit="#M"></rdg></app> pratyanta mlēccharājatanūjeyaruṁ <lb
	/>mūvatticchāsirvaravaruddha vāranārīnikāyamumantu tombattārusāsirva<lb break="no"
	/>rantaḥpurastrīyaruṁ mūvatticchāsirvar maigāpina gaṇabaddhadēvaruṁ mūvatti<lb break="no"
	/>cchāsirvar mūrdhābhiṣiktarappa mahāmakuṭabaddharumembattanālku lakke <lb
	/>bhadrahastiyuṁ tāvatpramitaṁ rathaṅgaḷuṁ padineṇṭukōṭi jātyaṁśvaṅgaḷu <lb
	/>membattanālkukōṭi padātiyuṁ mūvatticchāsira viṣayaṅgaḷumanite prasiddha<lb break="no"
	/>mahānagaraṅgaḷuṁ tombattāṟukōṭi grāmaṅgaḷumombaisāsiraṁ drōṇā<lb break="no"
	/>mukhaṅgaḷuṁ nālvatteṇsāsira paṭṭaṇaṅgaḷuṁ padināṟusāsira khēḍaṅgaḷuṁ <lb
	/>padinālsāsira saṁvāhanaṅgaḷumaivattāṟantaradvīpaṅgaḷumippatteṇsāsira durgaṁ <lb
	/>gaḷumaṟunūṟu kukṣikanivāsaṅgaḷuṁ daśasahasrakōṭi halaṅgaḷuṁ mūṟu <lb
	/>kōṭi gōmaṇḍalamuṁ dvādaśayōjana samutsarpadhvānaṅgaḷappānandabhēri<lb break="no"
	/>gaḷuṁ panneraḍuṁ bhērigaḷuṁ vijayaghōṣaṅgaḷemba panneraḍuṁ paṭahaṅgaḷuṁ <lb
	/>gambhīrāvartaṅgaḷembippattanālku śaṅkhaṅgaḷumambaraviḍambigaḷemba nālvatteṇṭu <lb
	/>kōṭi patākegaḷuṁ gaṅgātaraṅgadhavaḷaṅgaḷappanumagaḷemba mūvatteraḍu cāmaraṁ <lb
	/>gaḷuṁ ātmīya sakaḷa sāmrājyalakṣmīprakāśaṅgaḷāge</p>
	<lg n="4" met="mahāsragdhare">
	  <l>mu<app><lem>ḷi</lem><rdg wit="#M">ni</rdg></app>siṁ mēḷaisiyuṁ kāṇisalumiṟiyaluṁ <app><lem>pāḻi</lem><rdg wit="#M">paḷi</rdg></app>mādoṁ dharitrī</l>
	  <l>taḷadoḷ nirvyājaśauryaprakaṭitayaśanembannegaṁ caṇḍabāhā</l>
	  <l>baladiṁ pratyantabhūpāḷakaranibarumaṁ geldu ṣaṭkhaṇḍabhūmaṁ</l>
	  <l>ḍaḷamēkacchatramāgirpinamavayavadiṁ tāḷdidaṁ cakranāthaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="171"/>
	<lg n="5" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>anupama bhōjyapurīvā</l>
	  <l>hana nāṭakaratnanidhicamūgrahaśayyā</l>
	  <l>sanamene daśāṅgabhōgama</l>
	  <l>nanukarisidanadhiguṇapriyaṁ priyamitraṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antā mahārājādhirājananyasādhāraṇa daśāṅgabhōgamaniratanu<lb break="no"
	/>mapratimanātmīyaśāsananuṁ vajravr̥ṣabhanārāca śarīrasaṁhananuṁ samacaturasra<lb break="no"
	/>saṁsthānanuṁ pañcaśata śarāsanōtsēdhanuṁ svastika nandyāvartādi catuḥṣaṣṭi<lb break="no"
	/>lakṣaṇanuṁ apramitavīryanuṁ pūrvakōṭisaṁvatsarapramita paramāyuṣyanu<lb break="no"
	/>menisi nirantarameṇbattamūṟulakṣa pubbamarasugeyyuttamirdu</p>
	<lg n="6" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>tanniccheyindamorme ja</l>
	  <l>gannuta karakamalanesedu kaigeyyuttaṁ</l>
	  <l>kenneya nareyaṁ narapati</l>
	  <l>kannaḍiyoḷ tōṟe kaṇḍu vismayamuttaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antidircida jarāṅganādūti lalitamaṁ pottirda paḷitamaṁ kaṇḍu <lb
	/>tannagaloḷikkidōgaradoḷage kaṁ<app><lem>ḍa</lem><rdg wit="#M">ḍu</rdg></app>rōmakkēvayisuvantadakke kokkarisi vasu<lb break="no"
	/>matīrājyabhāramanabhiṣēkapūrvakaṁ sarvamitranembagraputranoḷ niyōjisi <lb
	/>dīkṣāgrahaṇatatparaṁ kṣēmaṅkaratīrthakara samavasaraṇamaṁ pokku bhuvanatraya<lb break="no"
	/>svāmige karaṇatrayaśuddhiyineṟagi dīkṣāprasādaṅgeyvudendu</p>
	<lg n="7" met="kandaṁ">
	  <l>sāsirvar nr̥pasutaroḍa</l>
	  <l>nā sakala vasundharādhināthaṁ mukti</l>
	  <l>śrīsatiyanolisalendu</l>
	  <l>dbhāsitaguṇamolidu dīkṣeyaṁ kaikoṇḍaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<p><label>va.</label>antu jinarūpamanā priyamitrabhūpaṁ kaikoṇḍanantaraṁ kṣētra<lb break="no"
	/>vāstu dhana dhānya dvipada catuṣpadaṁ yāna śayanāśana kupya bhāṇḍaprabhē<lb break="no"
	/>dadiṁ pattuṁ teṟada bāhyaparigrahamumaṁ mithyā krōdha māna māya lōbha<lb break="no"
	/>hāsya ratyarati śōka bhaya jugupse vēda rāga dvēṣagaḷemba padinālkumabhyaṁ <lb
	/>tara parigrahamumaṁ pattuviṭṭu daṇḍatyāgamindriyajaya kaṣāyavinigrahaṁ <pb n="172"
