	  <l><app><lem>didi</lem><rdg wit="#M">....di</rdg></app>raṁ bandudadondu gandhagajadantudgandhi mandāniḷaṁ</l>
	</lg>
	<pb n="207"/>
	<p><label>va.</label>ā nagōpatyakāntaprabhūta pavananidirgoṇḍoyye mellamella<lb break="no"
