	  <l>idu sakaḷajagatpāvana</l>
	  <l>midu paramajinēndra savanapīṭhaṁ tāneṁ</l>
	  <l>da<app><lem>da</lem><rdg wit="#M">danendulipudanudina</rdg></app>nodavi pudida mudadiṁ</l>
	  <l>pradakṣiṇaṅgeydudakhiḷa sura nikurambaṁ</l>
