	/>sōpānamārgadinoḷagaṁ pokku tadvibhūti viḷōkana janita vismayāpanna<lb break="no"
	/>mānasaruttuṅgapīḍatrayōpakaṇṭhamaneydi maṇimaya mahītaḷāliṅgita<lb break="no"
	/>sarvāṅgarāgi</p>
