	<p><label>va.</label>antu śatamakhaṁ mahāmakhamaṁ  mahāmahimeyiṁ māḍi <lb
	/>vaimānikāmarajanaparītanātmīyakōṣṭadoḷeḍeyaṟidippudumāviṣṭāṣṭā<lb break="no"
	/>tiśaya niyataparamalakṣmībhājanaṅge vinayōpanavanatāmaracaradanujavadā<lb break="no"
	/>sabhāsa<app><lem>bhā</lem><rdg wit="#M">bha</rdg></app>janaṅge dustara duranta<app><lem>madē</lem><rdg wit="#M">midai</rdg></app>kānta nayatimira nirasana prasanna<lb break="no"
	/>dhārācandraṅge sumatijinēndraṅge divyadhvani negaḻadirdudadaṟa kāraṇamē<lb break="no"
	/>nendu saṅkrandanaṁ nijāvadhiyaṁ prayōgisi tadarthāvadhāraṇa guṇasamarthana<lb break="no"
	/>ppagragaṇadharanillade poṟamaḍadirdudendaṟidu gaṇadharanuṁ gautamaneyappanendu <lb
	/>niścayisi kapaṭavaṭuvēṣadiṁ nimiṣamātradoḷe gautamagrāmakke vandu pañca<lb break="no"
	/>śatachātraparivr̥tanāgi vakhkhāṇisutirda gautamagōtramaṇḍananaṁ sūrya<lb break="no"
	/>vimānāṁśarāvatīrṇanapahasita gabhastimāḷiprabhāvitānananū <app><lem>na vāda</lem><rdg wit="#M">vā</rdg></app>nanaṁ <lb
	/>viprōttamanaṁ gautamanaṁ kāṇbudumā mahātmanettavōdappirēnimittaṁ bandi<lb break="no"
	/>rendu besagoḷe mahāvīranāsthānadoḷirdu nimmoḍane nuḍiva bageyiṁ <lb
	/>vādārthiyenāgi bandenendu jīvāditattvaprapañcānuyōgamaṁ prastuta<lb break="no"
	/>māge māḍi</p>
	<lg n="12" met="mattēbhavikrīḍitaṁ">
	  <l>todaḷuṇṭē kodaḷuṇṭe saṁśayapadaṁ mēṇuṇṭe <app><lem>vicchē</lem><rdg wit="#M">...cphō</rdg></app>dyameṁ</l>
